### Test 1: Predict for EXISTING customer (uses traditional + social)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "CUS123456",
  "features": {
    "traditional": [0.5, 0.8, 0.3, 0.7, 0.9, 0.2, 0.6, 0.4],
    "social": [0.6, 0.7, 0.5, 0.8, 0.4]
  }
}

### Test 2: Predict for NEW customer (uses xgboost only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "CUS999999",
  "features": {
    "xgboost": [0.5, 0.8, 0.3, 0.7, 0.9, 0.2, 0.6, 0.4, 0.5, 0.3]
  }
}

### Test 3: Search customer by ID (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/search?customer_id=CUS123456

### Test 4: Search customer by ID (POST)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "CUS123456"
}

### Test 5: Search non-existent customer
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/search?customer_id=CUSNOTFOUND

